task.summary:
Remove the ability to swipe to refresh
The swipe to refresh makes the UI too complicated, and it is not worth it.
Fix missing elevation in AppBarLayout on Android 4.2
Change the main activity to have only one instance
Fix the blank space above the list in settings
Change the default on launch tab to be the current day
Add hamburger action on the toolbar to open the navigation drawer
Change App to only refresh data when the user changed class
Change ScheduleFragment to only refresh when the user changes the class in settings
Remove hamburger to back arrow animation
Change the app to not sync schedule in first launch before class is set
Add the abnormal classes to the class database
